WEBVTT

00:07.750 --> 00:08.750
Perfect!

00:09.959 --> 00:11.291
Aw, yeah!

00:11.834 --> 00:15.166
Almost ready for our special movie time.

00:15.166 --> 00:18.125
Ooh, I'll go get our snuggling blanket.

00:19.125 --> 00:22.208
And now for the final touch.

00:22.208 --> 00:23.208
Snacks!

00:24.250 --> 00:26.041
<i>Weather alert, there's a giant storm</i>

00:26.041 --> 00:28.041
<i>sweeping in from off the coast.</i>

00:29.375 --> 00:30.375
Mmm?

00:31.417 --> 00:32.875
Wha...

00:32.875 --> 00:34.083
No snacks?

00:34.083 --> 00:35.917
Movie time will be ruined!

00:35.917 --> 00:37.250
Minnie!

00:37.834 --> 00:40.375
<i>Seriously. Don't go outside!</i>

00:40.375 --> 00:41.500
Mickey!

00:46.625 --> 00:49.250
Hold it! I know what to do.

00:49.250 --> 00:50.709
Oh, thank goodness!

00:50.709 --> 00:51.917
You hang tight

00:51.917 --> 00:53.375
and I'll get more snacks.

00:53.375 --> 00:54.500
What?

00:54.500 --> 00:55.500
Mickey, no...

00:56.041 --> 00:57.125
Mickey!

00:58.625 --> 00:59.959
Wait!

00:59.959 --> 01:01.250
Oh!

01:08.125 --> 01:09.500
Where the heck are you going?

01:09.500 --> 01:11.125
To save movie time.

01:12.208 --> 01:13.125
Ooh, a nickel!

01:18.166 --> 01:19.458
Listen, buddy.

01:19.458 --> 01:20.959
I'm closing up shop!

01:20.959 --> 01:21.959
Two seconds!

01:23.083 --> 01:25.667
What do you think?
Salty or sweet?

01:29.625 --> 01:30.709
Yeah, you're right.

01:30.709 --> 01:32.166
I should just get both.

01:32.959 --> 01:34.709
Hey, pal! Okie dokie, I'm a...

01:34.709 --> 01:36.667
Pull your head out of your shorts.

01:36.667 --> 01:38.250
There's a storm coming!

01:39.000 --> 01:40.000
Ah...

01:46.834 --> 01:48.625
There's a storm coming!

01:54.625 --> 01:56.208
Forget movie time,

01:56.208 --> 01:57.750
I've got to save minnie!

02:02.667 --> 02:04.291
Sorry!
Excuse me!

02:09.208 --> 02:11.542
Uh...
Excuse me?

02:20.667 --> 02:22.458
I'm coming, minnie!

02:34.583 --> 02:36.166
Oh, no. Hail.

02:41.792 --> 02:42.875
Whoa!

02:48.166 --> 02:49.709
Whoo!
Whoo-hoo!

02:50.959 --> 02:52.375
Minnie's house!

02:59.041 --> 03:00.709
Minn...
Mickey!

03:00.959 --> 03:02.917
Mickey!

03:02.917 --> 03:04.667
I'm here to rescue you...

03:06.709 --> 03:07.709
Huh?

03:08.208 --> 03:09.250
Oh...

03:18.333 --> 03:21.208
Well, at least we still have movie time.

03:22.583 --> 03:25.417
Yeah, now if we only had some
place to plug this in...

03:26.959 --> 03:27.959
Perfect!
